{"tid":1628454,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"全面停止分化","createTime":"2019-10-06T02:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T03:43:06.000Z","uid":183680,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"16b4d6a8ef73e1aac9194646589c0b5154abc85f","tid":1628454,"uid":183680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:58:30.000Z","msg":"因為小小裝修 神獸問問<br />\n成個熱門都係啲分化po<br />\n啲人一見到意見不合就<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">起哂鋼</span></span><br />\n唔排除係有人別有用心<br />\n但我地自己心態唔正確都有可能<br />\n運動一開始冇大台 <br />\n就係想大家都有<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">獨立思考</span></span><br />\n大家裝修之前<br />\n唔該諗下咁做係唔係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對凖政權</span></span><br />\n爭取緊<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求</span></span>嘅邊一樣<br />\n有意請要提出討論 而唔係互屌<br />\n今日唔理你讚唔讚成裝修 神獸<br />\n街頭見 2PM SOGO<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ffc903da9e2cb47abcad89fa2ab495e9f12068c5","tid":1628454,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T02:58:43.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyYDlCk4w_-I&d=15TDSCYqMG0%2FxcOE0oxfEAzuSh5pVPBxDrYQpIU1Wbo%3D&h=cfdfdbc5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I</a>"},{"pid":"fac1e33f4344faeeff15efff4481dcab7882d526","tid":1628454,"uid":116491,"like":1,"dislike":0